Competency required for this project is:

Experience with Rpi GPIO
Understand external power requirement when adding new peripherials to RPI!
Connection of PIR sensor to the RPI board
Connection and configuration of GSM900 module with RPI 
Understanding and using AT commands
Software language skill can be managed.

